sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant A as Agent
    participant SL as Skill Loader<br/>(/home/z/my-project/skills/)
    participant IG as ID Graph<br/>(verify-id-graph.js)
    participant S as Standard<br/>(standards/*.md)
    participant R as Rule<br/>(guard/rules/*.md)

    Note over U,A: User asks Agent to perform a task
    U->>A: "Implement feature X"

    Note over A: Agent consults workflow-discipline<br/>skill (RULE-MONOLITH-001)<br/>before acting
    A->>SL: Skill(command="workflow-discipline_sts")
    SL-->>A: SKILL.md loaded

    Note over A: Skill says: check standards<br/>before writing code
    A->>IG: query Related: edges for STD-FE-001

    Note over IG: ID graph has 60 nodes<br/>and 111 edges<br/>(G01-G15 invariant: all resolve)
    IG-->>A: Related: STD-ARCH-001, STD-A11Y-001<br/>Aligned_with: ZAI-FS-001

    A->>S: open STD-FE-001 (frontend)
    S-->>A: §2 anti-monolith thresholds<br/>§11 design system delegation

    Note over A: FE-001 §11 delegates to<br/>DESIGN-001 — Agent must follow<br/>the Related: edge
    A->>S: open STD-DESIGN-001
    S-->>A: §4 color tokens<br/>§11 animation tokens

    Note over A: FE-001 §11 references<br/>RULE-MONOLITH-002 (size cap)
    A->>R: open RULE-MONOLITH-002
    R-->>A: hard limit 250 lines/file

    Note over A: Now Agent has full context<br/>across 3 layers + 1 rule
    A->>A: write code compliant<br/>with all 4 sources

    A-->>U: implementation + citation<br/>of STD-FE-001 §2.1, RULE-MONOLITH-002
